{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What's happening to the climate?"},{"time":2000,"text":"It is unbelievably bad."},{"time":4000,"text":"This is, obviously, that famous view now of the Arctic,"},{"time":7000,"text":"which is likely to be gone at this point"},{"time":9000,"text":"in the next three or four or five years. Very, very, very scary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"So we all look at what we can do."},{"time":14000,"text":"And when you look at the worldwide sources of CO2,"},{"time":16000,"text":"52 percent are tied to buildings."},{"time":18000,"text":"Only nine percent is passenger cars, interestingly enough."},{"time":21000,"text":"So we ran off to a sushi bar."},{"time":23000,"text":"And at that sushi bar we came up with a great idea."},{"time":25000,"text":"And it was something called EcoRock."},{"time":27000,"text":"And we said we could redesign the 115-year-old"},{"time":30000,"text":"gypsum drywall process that generates"},{"time":32000,"text":"20 billion pounds of CO2 a year."},{"time":34000,"text":"So it was a big idea. We wanted to reduce that by 80 percent,"},{"time":37000,"text":"which is exactly what we've done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"We started R&amp;D in 2006."},{"time":41000,"text":"Decided to use recycled content from cement"},{"time":43000,"text":"and steel manufacturing."},{"time":45000,"text":"There is the inside of our lab. We haven't shown this before."},{"time":47000,"text":"But our people had to do some 5,000"},{"time":50000,"text":"different mixes to get this right, to hit our targets."},{"time":55000,"text":"And they worked absolutely very, very, very hard."},{"time":57000,"text":"So then we went forward and built our production line in China."},{"time":60000,"text":"We don't build this production equipment any longer in the U.S., unfortunately."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"We did the line install over the summer."},{"time":65000,"text":"We started right there, with absolutely nothing."},{"time":67000,"text":"You're seeing for the first time, a brand new drywall production line,"},{"time":71000,"text":"not made using gypsum at all."},{"time":73000,"text":"That's the finished production line there."},{"time":75000,"text":"We got our first panel out on December third."},{"time":77000,"text":"That is the slurry being poured onto paper, basically. That's the line running."},{"time":81000,"text":"The exciting thing is, look at the faces of the people."},{"time":84000,"text":"These are people who worked this project for two to three years."},{"time":86000,"text":"And they are so excited. That's the first board off the line."},{"time":89000,"text":"Our Vice President of Operation kissing the board. Obviously very, very excited."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"But this has a huge, huge impact on the environment."},{"time":96000,"text":"We signed the first panel just a few weeks after that, had a great signing ceremony,"},{"time":100000,"text":"leading to people hopefully using these products across the world."},{"time":104000,"text":"And we've got Cradle-to-Cradle Gold on this thing."},{"time":106000,"text":"We happened to win, just recently, the Green Product of the Year"},{"time":108000,"text":"for \"The Re-Invention of Drywall,\" from Popular Science."},{"time":111000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."},{"time":113000,"text":"So here is what we learned: 8,000 gallons of gas"},{"time":116000,"text":"equivalent to build one house."},{"time":118000,"text":"You probably had no idea. It's like driving around the world six times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"We must change everything."},{"time":122000,"text":"Look around the room: chairs, wood,"},{"time":125000,"text":"everything around us has to change or we're not going to lick this problem."},{"time":128000,"text":"Don't listen to the people who say you can't do this, because anyone can."},{"time":131000,"text":"And these job losses, we can fix them with green-collar jobs."},{"time":134000,"text":"We've got four plants. We're building this stuff around the country."},{"time":136000,"text":"We're going as fast as we can."},{"time":138000,"text":"Two and a half million cars worth of gypsum,"},{"time":141000,"text":"you know, CO2 generated. Right?"},{"time":143000,"text":"So what will you do? I'll tell you what I did and why I did it. And I know my time's up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Those are my kids, Natalie and David."},{"time":148000,"text":"When they have their kids, 2050,"},{"time":150000,"text":"they'd better look back at Grandpa and say,"},{"time":152000,"text":"\"Hey, you gave it a good shot. You did the best you could"},{"time":154000,"text":"with the team that you had.\""},{"time":156000,"text":"So my hope is that when you leave TED,"},{"time":159000,"text":"you will look at reducing your carbon footprint"},{"time":161000,"text":"in however you can do it."},{"time":163000,"text":"And if you don't know how, please find me -- I will help you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"Last but not least, Bill Gates, I know you invented Windows."},{"time":169000,"text":"Wait till you see, maybe next year, what kind of windows we've invented."},{"time":172000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":174000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}